# Official raspberrypi/pico-sdk checkout (currently tag 2.3.0) plus its
# own nested submodules (tinyusb/cyw43-driver/lwip/mbedtls/btstack) -
# ~675MB, versioned, and meant to live outside any one project's repo
# (PICO_SDK_PATH is exactly for this). See CLAUDE.md for how to fetch
# the matching version.
pico-sdk

# Copyrighted HP-41 ROM firmware dumps and the generated C source that
# re-encodes them - not ours to redistribute. Each user must supply
# their own legally-obtained ROM files here; see roms/README.md.
roms/*.ROM
roms/*.rom
roms/rom_images.c

# sim/'s host-file-backed continuous-memory snapshot - local runtime
# state, not source, same treatment as roms/rom_images.c above.
sim/soynut_sim_persist.bin
